---
title: Slow-Cooked Pork Meatball Ragu with Mash & Parmesan Cheese
description: Our Slow Cook recipes are perfect for those cold nights - switch on your oven and get ready to cook low and slow to pack maximum flavour. We love a little ball of deliciousness and a meatball fits this description perfectly. Slow-cooked pork with a hint of our garlic
and herb seasoning is rolled up nice and tight, stirred through a saucy veggie ragu and placed on top of a pillow of buttery
mashed potatoes.

